      <title>短期覆盖在最近的股票市场篮板之下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/short-covering-is-lying-beneath-the-recent-stock-market-rebounds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[S＆amp; p 500指数本周每天都开始对贸易战的担忧和经济增长放缓，只是为了恢复并陷入绿色。虽然股票市场的动作并不总是很清楚，但这些举动下的罪魁祸首是罪魁祸首：短期覆盖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/short-covering-is-lying-beneath-the-recent-stock-market-rebounds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 18:02:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
